{"tid":2425244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺旺角站試過俾變態佬整濕條褲","createTime":"2021-02-27T08:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T09:25:18.000Z","uid":247187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b88ba5357e5f690fef06327e4f9f43251614319c","tid":2425244,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"代友開 <br />\n<br />\n日期：2月6號 <br />\n時間：大約 4:15-4:30<br />\n地點：旺角MTR E2出口<br />\n<br />\n我嗰日着緊一件白色T-shirt ，橙色外搭背心 ，長牛仔褲<br />\n<br />\n我嗰日同一個朋友準備由地鐵路面出口行落去，人流都幾多，大家前後左右相隔大約半個手臂位 。<br />\n<br />\n我突然feel到pat pat 有啲濕同熱，好似漏M咁 。之後我發現真係濕咗一part，大約一個半手掌。 <br />\n<br />\n我即刻望向後面，同企正我後面個男人對視左，之後我停低，同完朋友解釋完咩事之後 (大約10秒到 )，我就見到嗰個男人入咗MTR。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻衝落去mtr 入閘附近叫停佢，我問佢(我唔係好記得實質字眼，但同樣意思）<br />\n<br />\n「先生 我想問我條褲係咪你整到咁」<br />\n「唔係呀」<br />\n我諗緊會唔會係佢有水樽裝住啲液體，所以就望住佢手抽嘅袋<br />\n「先生 你可唔可打開個袋俾我睇」<br />\n佢打開咗之後，嗰袋裝住係幾件衫，之後佢就入閘走咗。其實佢仲有一個背囊，但我嗰時個腦load唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我就去咗MTR個廁所抹下條褲，液體個量係有少少濕到我條底褲，無味，隻色都冇話好明顯。<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係好肯定呢啲係咩液體，亦都唔肯定係咪嗰個男人整，但呢件事令我好困擾。<br />\n<br />\n有冇絲打有同樣遭遇<br />\n<br />\n屌好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ced13d96981de12fb1ea40a45358a5ef4077587","tid":2425244,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81558df78586fd508b3372a2e797170c9150dd67","tid":2425244,"uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"「先生 我想問我條褲係咪你整到咁」<br />\n<br />\n以為睇緊國產凌凌漆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e35deb1995bce41eb3eff7771dea2633e9c742f","tid":2425244,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"之前有絲打開過po<br />\n應該慣犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dedf0bda3bdab9c29434581065f82cd5de8f292","tid":2425244,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"唔係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係旺角"},{"pid":"61f7e3d102e3e0dd04dea578fe31ede5e7550f2d","tid":2425244,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過真係唔係個條油整<br />\n個下又check唔到"},{"pid":"754daff0c729991d05e1f721759cf4fbcfada5a4","tid":2425244,"uid":67116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"如果係牛仔褲<br />\n咁應該要好多水先透到"},{"pid":"5c23a3c3583f9ab19a390ffa7d7aa452e40b74ca","tid":2425244,"uid":241449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"22ffc69030e04410b9d8b863988974fe5130a80e","tid":2425244,"uid":20464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"81558df78586fd508b3372a2e797170c9150dd67","tid":2425244,"uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"「先生 我想問我條褲係咪你整到咁」<br />\n<br />\n以為睇緊國產凌凌漆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"係呀，點呢，有咩問題呢 ？"},{"pid":"f98fcd620a3efb348ddc717e887d812f302eafe6","tid":2425244,"uid":58880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"係唔係精黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264c0352b5dbf291dc5fb3a840f03aba5b4a0094","tid":2425244,"uid":252678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"22ffc69030e04410b9d8b863988974fe5130a80e","tid":2425244,"uid":20464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8